We brought our 4 month old Great Pyrenees puppy last year & had no problem
dog wise.  However, he was more appropriate than some of the adjacent
campers. Not sure I will convince the wife to accompany moi again this year,
but the dog wants to go!

This is in no way meant to disparage the Jamboree, which is the biggest/most
organized/ fun bus campout I attend each year, but if you are in the wrong
neighborhood at Jerome, it can be eye opening.

FWIW,

Tom Buese-going again this year in the DC
